OL,6,FA paedophile who fled the country
OL,7,Fduring a trial which ended with his
OL,8,Fconviction for child sex offences has
OL,9,Fbeen arrested at Manchester Airport.
OL,11,FHassan Mahmood, 24, from Bury, was
OL,12,Fheld after stepping off a flight on
OL,13,FMonday 29 September.
OL,15,FMahmood, of Gigg Lane, Bury, was found
OL,16,Fguilty on four counts of child sexual
OL,17,Foffences following a trial in August.
OL,18,FHe absconded on the second day of the
OL,19,Fcase, which continued in his absence.
OL,20,FIt is believed he fled to Pakistan.
