OL,6,FHe was found guilty of engaging in
OL,7,Fpenetrative sexual activity with a
OL,8,Fchild; causing a child to watch/look
OL,9,Fat an image of sexual activity;
OL,10,Fengaging in sexual activity in
OL,11,Fpresence of a child; and engaging in
OL,12,Fsexual communication with a child.
OL,14,FThe victim was a girl under 16 at the
OL,15,Ftime. The court heard she told Mahmood
OL,16,Fhow old she was. He was sentenced to
OL,17,Ffive-and-a-half years in prison in his
OL,18,Fabsence.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
