OL,6,FAddressing him as though he were
OL,7,Fpresent, Judge John Potter said during
OL,8,Fthe sentencing hearing: "At that time,
OL,9,Fyou knew she was still a child. You
OL,10,Fwere 20 years of age. You knew she was
OL,11,Fa child because she told you on a
OL,12,Fchat."
OL,14,FThe court heard Mahmood 'sexually
OL,15,Fexploited' the girl for his own
OL,16,F'sexual gratification'. Messages were
OL,17,Fexchanged on Snapchat that became
OL,18,F'sexualised' from February 2022,
OL,19,Faccording to the prosecution.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
