OL,6,FMahmood sent her 'graphic images and
OL,7,Flanguage' as well as sexually explicit
OL,8,Fvideos of himself. The court heard
OL,9,Fthere were also FaceTime chats between
OL,10,Fthem. In one, Mahmood positioned his
OL,11,Fcamera so she could see him carrying
OL,12,Fout a sex act.
OL,14,FThe court heard that after his arrest,
OL,15,FMahmood, who had no previous
OL,16,Fconvictions, sent the girl a 'vile,
OL,17,Fdisgusting, abusive and demeaning'
OL,18,Fletter in which he told her to kill
OL,19,Fherself because of her 'snitching'.
OL,20,F"She was not intimidated by it," said
OL,21,FJudge Potter.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
