OL,6,FFollowing the arrest, Detective
OL,7,FConstable Shaheen Saleh, of GMP's
OL,8,FChild Criminal Exploitation Team,
OL,9,Fsaid: "Mahmood cowardly left the
OL,10,Fcountry to evade punishment for his
OL,11,Fvile crimes, and I am glad he will now
OL,12,Fbe behind bars where he belongs.
OL,14,F"We are committed to locking up those
OL,15,Fresponsible for child sexual offences,
OL,16,Fand we will always ensure that they
OL,17,Fare brought to justice, no matter
OL,18,Fwhere they try to hide.
